graph TD
    User((User)) -->|Query| Router{Query Router}
    Router -->|Simple| SLM[Small Language Model]
    Router -->|Complex| Planner[Agentic Planner]
    
    subgraph Agentic_Loop
        Planner -->|Action| Tools[Tool/API Access]
        Tools -->|Result| Critic[Outcome Critic]
        Critic -->|Iterate| Planner
    end
    
    Critic -->|Final Answer| User
    SLM --> User
